    {
      "scene_index": 2,
      "label": "第二场",
      "characters_present": [
        "报子"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖风入松〗。报子上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "报子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺，曹丞相麾下探事军官是也。探得袁绍命大将颜良以为先锋，统大兵十万进"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [],
      "stats": {
        "line_counts": {
          "stage_direction": 2,
          "白": 1
        },
        "singing_ratio": 0.0,
        "dominant_style_family": null,
        "musical_styles": []
      }
    },
    {
      "scene_index": 3,
      "label": "第三场",
      "characters_present": [
        "宋宪",
        "张辽",
        "徐晃",
        "报子",
        "探子",
        "曹操",
        "程昱",
        "许褚",
        "魏绩"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（曹八将、四上手、四龙套、曹操同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "引子",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "文韬武略，辅佐汉朝，比周公，谋高计巧，灭群雄如削草，统雄师，烟尘齐扫。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "朝朝虎帐夜谈兵，纷纷宇宙何日平。身系安危吾肩重，愿做霖雨沛苍生。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老夫曹操。闻得袁绍，起兵前来谋窥许昌。特此统领兵将，前来白马坡地方扎\n营，以观动静。曾命探子哨探，未见回报。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（报子上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "报子",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "打听军情事，报与丞相知。"
        },
        {
          "character": "报子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "报，探子告进。丞相在上，探子叩首。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "探听袁绍人马如何？"
        },
        {
          "character": "探子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "袁绍命大将颜良为先锋，统领大兵十万，来犯白马坡。特来报知。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "赏你金牌，再去哨探。"
        },
        {
          "character": "探子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "得令！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（报子下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来，吩咐随营将官听点。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（起鼓点名。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众将官，颜良乃河北名将，今为先锋前来，休得视为小敌。听我号令！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖玉芙蓉〗。报子上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "报子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "颜良讨战。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "再探。"
        },
        {
          "character": "报子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "得令！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（报子下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "颜良讨战，哪位将军出马？"
        },
        {
          "character": "宋宪、魏绩",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "丞相，我二人情愿出马，立斩颜良。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好，须要小心。"
        },
        {
          "character": "宋宪、魏绩",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "得令！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（宋宪、魏绩同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "宋宪、魏绩乃吕布手下之勇将，此番出马，定斩颜良。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（曹操看。三冲头。报子上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "报子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "报，宋宪、魏绩被颜良刀劈马下。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "再探！"
        },
        {
          "character": "报子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "得令！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（报子下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀呀，可叹二位将军，命丧颜良之手。不知何人能敌颜良？"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐晃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "丞相但放宽心，末将不才，情愿立斩颜良。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将军出马，留心在意。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐晃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "得令！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（徐晃下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "徐晃出马，不知胜负如何。且听探马一报。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（三冲头。报子上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "报子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "启丞相：徐晃被颜良砍伤左膀，败回营来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "快快抬往后营，好好医治。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（龙套抬徐晃同上，过场，同下。众将同惊。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "唉，幸喜伤了左膀，不致伤命。颜良如此英雄，连伤数将，这便怎么处？"
        },
        {
          "character": "程昱",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "启禀丞相：程昱保举一人，能敌颜良。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "所举何人？"
        },
        {
          "character": "程昱",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "非关羽不可。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我也知非他不可，恐他立功便想辞去。"
        },
        {
          "character": "程昱",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "想刘玄德若在，必投袁绍。今若使关羽斩了颜良，袁绍必疑玄德而杀之矣。玄\n德既死，关羽又何往哉？"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哈哈哈！借关羽之手，以杀玄德。程昱此计甚佳！\n张辽听令！命你速去请关羽前来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张辽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "得令！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（张辽下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "许褚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "丞相，想俺曹营，岂无杀退颜良之人，何必去请关羽，俺许褚情愿出马，去战\n颜良。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "仲康既要出马，我带领兵将，在土山之上观战，以助将军之威。须要小心在意。"
        },
        {
          "character": "许褚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "丞相但放宽心，俺定斩颜良之首级，献与丞相。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（许褚下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "许褚虽然英勇，恐亦不能胜过颜良。\n众将官，随我去到白马坡上，观战去者。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "英雄虽非蠢袁绍，\n他地广兵强将也骁。\n不可大意我要运略韬。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人同下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
