    {
      "scene_index": 7,
      "label": "第七场",
      "characters_present": [
        "众将",
        "关羽",
        "曹操",
        "程昱",
        "颜良",
        "颜良已斩兵将散"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（颜良、四龙套同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "颜良",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "曹操被某杀破胆，\n并无有一人到阵前。\n颜良要战你们哪一个敢？"
        },
        {
          "character": "颜良",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哈……谁敢来，谁敢来？"
        },
        {
          "character": "颜良",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "得意洋洋站土山。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（关羽上，斩颜良。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "赤兔追风快如闪，\n青龙偃月饱血餐。\n报效曹公第一番！（下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "颜良已斩兵将散、曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "颜良已斩兵将散、曹操",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "遥望刀光猛一闪，\n颜良尸首落雕鞍？"
        },
        {
          "character": "颜良已斩兵将散、曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众将，你们可曾看见云长斩颜良么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "众将",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我等俱已看见。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "看得可真？"
        },
        {
          "character": "众将",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "明明白白看见刀起，颜良首级落下。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哈哈哈，我好喜也！颜良已死，袁绍，袁绍，你命休矣！"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "这等神勇世上罕，\n刀光闪处人马翻。\n捧酒下山迎好汉——"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（曹操下山。关羽上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "丞相虎威得胜还。\n献上首级请观看！"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "将军武艺果不凡！"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "看酒来，将军，暂饮此酒，以贺大功！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖小吹打〗。关羽接酒，谢天地，坐下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将军真乃虎将也！"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "某何足道哉！我三弟张翼德，于万马军中，取上将之首级，如探囊取物一般！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众将同惊。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "唔呼呀，这样的英勇，还不足为奇，张翼德，在万马军中，取上将之首级，如\n探囊取物一般，不可轻视。\n取笔砚过来，记在袍襟之下，日后遇张莫战。尔等也记下了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "程昱",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "笔墨在此。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众将官，快快写好了！\n颜良已灭，河北兵将败走。我今保奏关将军，进爵汉寿亭侯之职，请到大营设\n筵贺功。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人同下。）"
        }
      ],
